questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Study the table given below and answer the question. The table shows the sale and profits of Company X.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
