&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concept used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Count the policies of different years of each branches. check the above given condition. the pairs of branches have least count will be the .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Total number of policies of branch A = 53 + 34 + 54 + 54 + 76 = 271&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch B&amp;nbsp;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;23 + 57 + 65 + 25 + 45 = 215&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch C&amp;nbsp;= 54 + 54 + 56 + 76 + 34 = 274&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch D&amp;nbsp;= 26 + 25 + 45 + 65 + 48 = 209&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch E&amp;nbsp;= 64 + 76 + 76 + 92 + 90 = 398&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch F&amp;nbsp;= 35 + 45 + 56 + 45 + 76 = 257&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch G&amp;nbsp;= 62 + 52 +45 + 65 + 45 = 269&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total number of policies of branch H&amp;nbsp;= 55 + 13 + 76 + 92 + 34 = 270&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Now counting the policies of pair branches given in options,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 1 :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

